net.sf.beezle.mork.compiler

Class Stubs

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.beezle.mork.compiler.Stubs

  • public class Stubs
extends Object
    Helper functions referred by Mapper.mapper. These methods brigde gaps between references in mork files and the functionality in the classes. In the long run, this class should vanish as I provide more and more powerful mapping features.
